column1: There is also a tier list for reverse image. Google is the worst, it just is. SauceNao and Tineye are both super specific with images. Bing sometimes comes in handy but is ultimately not great. But Yandex? Yandex gets the job done right. It is a double edged sword however because some of the results come up in Russian
